NK041(di)041:1: // skong gi bshad pa mdor bsdus su byas pa bzhugs so //
NK041(di)041:3: he ru ka dpal dkyil 'khor kun gyi gtso //
NK041(di)041:4: tha dad ma dmigs rje btsun gter bdag gling //
NK041(di)041:5: gang gi zhabs pad spyi bor rtag mchod nas //
NK041(di)041:6: skong chen bzhi yi bshad pa mdo tsam bri //
NK041(di)041:7: de la spyir thugs dam skong bar byed pa'i cho ga la /
NK041(di)041:8: nyams chag gi skong chen lnga ste /
NK041(di)041:13: 'gyod tshangs bshags pa'i skong ba rnams su grags pa las /
NK041(di)041:14: 'dir na rag dong sprugs mtshams med lnga sbyong gi dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga la /
NK041(di)041:15: shing rta chen po slob dpon so so'i dgongs pa /
NK041(di)041:16: zhi khro rgyud lung gi rang gzhung sdebs pa la /
NK041(di)041:17: dong sprugs kyi kha skong ba zhi khro rab 'byams su grags pa dang /
NK041(di)041:18: yi ge brgya pa phrin las kyi rgyud kyi dgongs
NK041(di)041:19: pa brgya ldan las rim gyi man ngag gis bkral
NK041(di)041:20: ba rigs brgya'i dkyil 'khor rigs bdag gcig gis bsdus
NK041(di)041:21: pa zhi khro rigs bsdus su grags pa dang /
NK041(di)041:22: glang po che rab 'bogs kyi rgyud las bkol ba
NK041(di)041:23: kalpa dum bu'i rgyud dri med bshags rgyud la brten
NK041(di)041:24: pa rigs so sor phye ba'i dkyil 'khor zhi khro
NK041(di)041:25: khrom sprugs su grags pa dang /
NK041(di)041:26: bshags rgyud kyi le'u gsum pa phyag gi bkol byang
NK041(di)041:27: ltar zhi khro gnas bsgyur gyi gleng gzhi ji skad
NK041(di)041:28: smos pa'i rim pa bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la brten
NK041(di)041:29: pa zhi khro gnas bsgyur du grags pa ste /
NK041(di)041:30: de ltar bzhed tshul bzhi las /
NK041(di)041:31: 'dir slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dgongs pa dang
NK041(di)041:32: khyad par slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi
NK041(di)041:33: man ngag sogs rgya bod kyi gzhung rnying ma rnams
NK041(di)041:34: kyi dgongs pa rgyud lung man ngag gi gnad thams
NK041(di)041:35: cad gcig tu bsdus pa gter chen chos kyi rgyal
NK041(di)041:36: po gter bdag gling pas mdzad pa na rag dong
NK041(di)041:37: sprugs 'khor ba kun grol zhes zhi khro rab 'byams
NK041(di)041:38: kyi dkyil 'khor chen po la brten nas /
NK041(di)041:39: rtog tshogs lha'i rang bzhin gdod ma nas rnam par
NK041(di)041:40: dag pa'i sgrub gzhi nyid dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor
NK041(di)041:41: du gsal gdab pa la mkha' khyab 'bras bu'i ye
NK041(di)041:42: shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang dbyer med du byed pa'i
NK041(di)041:43: thabs la brten nas nang phung po rten gyi bshags
NK041(di)041:44: pa dang / phyag gi bkol byang la brten nas 'gyod tshig gi bshags pa dang /
NK041(di)041:45: skong chen bzhi gnas dag gnas gyur dang bcas pas phyi yo byad tshogs kyi bshags pa dang /
NK041(di)041:46: bdag 'jug dang 'brel bar mkha' 'gro ma gtor ma'i
NK041(di)041:47: dbang dang rig pa'i rtsal dbang la brten nas gsang
NK041(di)041:48: ba byang chub sems kyi bshags pa ste /
NK041(di)041:49: de ltar bshags pa'i thabs rmad du byung ba rnam pa bzhi las /
NK041(di)041:50: 'dir skong chen bzhi dag gyur dang bcas pas phyi yo byad tshogs bsog gi bshags pa la /
NK041(di)041:51: mchod pa'i yo byad bshams tshul dang /
NK041(di)041:54: sman gtor rak+ta sgron me'i mchod pa bzhi'i bshams tshul /
NK041(di)041:56: de nyid rang byung rang shar gyi tshul du 'bul tshul dang gsum las /
NK041(di)041:58: gang du stegs bu gru bzhi pa bcas pa'i g.yas
NK041(di)041:59: g.yon mdun gsum gyi ngos bang rim can byas pa'i
NK041(di)041:60: steng zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor chu tshon gyis bris pa
NK041(di)041:61: bshams pa'i stegs bu'i rgyab stegs mtho ba la bdag
NK041(di)041:62: bskyed zhi khro'i gtor ma zlum po sbo ldir can
NK041(di)041:63: la lha grangs dang ldan pa'i mtheb kyus bskor ba'i
NK041(di)041:64: g.yas g.yon du sman dang rak+ta bcas bshams /
NK041(di)041:65: dkyil 'khor gyi mdun dbus su mkha' 'gro'i gtor ma
NK041(di)041:66: bla gtor lta bu la phyogs bzhir pad 'dab gyen
NK041(di)041:67: langs kyi mtshams mtheb kyus gcer ba'i steng du ril
NK041(di)041:69: bsdu na de'i g.yas su zhi ba'i gtor ma dkar
NK041(di)041:70: po sbo ldir can gyi rtsa bar mtheb kyu zhe
NK041(di)041:72: g.yon du khro gtor dpal gtor can gyi rtsa bar
NK041(di)041:73: mtheb kyu nga brgyad kyis bskor ba bshams pa'i g.yas
NK041(di)041:74: g.yon du sman raka bcas bshams pas 'thus /
NK041(di)041:75: rgyas par byed na zhi khro'i gtor ma lha grangs
NK041(di)041:76: dang mnyam pa bshams tshul stegs bu'i ngos kyi bang
NK041(di)041:77: rim dang po'i g.yas kyi char zhi gtor g.yon gyi
NK041(di)041:78: cha la khro gtor bshams pa'o //
NK041(di)041:79: da lta phyag bzhes su bang rim dang por zhi gtor /
NK041(di)041:81: gsum par bdud rtsi lha grangs dang mnyam pa /
NK041(di)041:82: bzhi par rak+ta yang de mtshungs /
NK041(di)041:83: lnga pa sogs yod na mar me lha grangs dang mnyam pa /
NK041(di)041:84: med na mdun gyi mthil du bshams pa'o //
NK041(di)041:85: gang ltar yang mchod pa rnams gtsang sbra dang ldan pas bkod legs par bshams pa yin no //
NK041(di)041:87: dang po bdud rtsi'i go don ni /
NK041(di)041:88: de yang don yin lugs kyi dbang du byas pa'i bdud rtsi ni /
NK041(di)041:89: 'khor 'das thams cad ye nas bdud rtsi'i ngo bor gnas pa ste /
NK041(di)041:91: srid gsum ye nas bdud rtsi lnga //
NK041(di)041:92: ma bcos lhun grub rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK041(di)041:94: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK041(di)041:95: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK041(di)041:97: dam rdzas bdud rtsi zhes grags pa ni /
NK041(di)041:98: rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK041(di)041:99: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK041(di)041:100: dag pa'i snod chu mi 'dor ro //
NK041(di)041:101: zhes gsungs pas bdud rtsi lnga yin la /
NK041(di)041:102: de'i skyob dang 'phrad du gyur pa'i rdzas rnams la ni sman bdud rtsi zhes grags te /
NK041(di)041:103: de ltar rtsa ba dang skyob rnams tshang bar sbyar ba ni /
NK041(di)041:104: rtsa brgyad yan lag stong sbyar a mri ta zhes /
NK041(di)041:105: bdud rtsi lnga'i rtsa ba brgyad la'ang /
NK041(di)041:106: sngon byung gi rtsa ba brgyad /
NK041(di)041:110: zug pa rtsa ba'i rtsa ba brgyad /
NK041(di)041:111: 'dril ba sdong po'i rtsa ba brgyad /
NK041(di)041:112: gyes pa yan lag gi rtsa ba brgyad /
NK041(di)041:113: smin pa 'bras bu'i rtsa ba brgyad de /
NK041(di)041:114: de ltar bdud rtsi'i rtsa ba brgyad brgyad drug cu re bzhi yod par grags /
NK041(di)041:116: bdud rtsi lnga po re re la nang tshan brgya brgya yod pa rnams bsdoms pas lnga brgya dang /
NK041(di)041:117: de re re'i skyob lnga brgya rnams bsdoms pas stong
NK041(di)041:118: du tshang ba tshul bzhin du sbyar nas bsgrubs pa
NK041(di)041:119: 'di la bdud rtsi a mri ta zhes /
NK041(di)041:120: bod skad du 'chi med kyi rdzas /
NK041(di)041:121: ra sa ya na zhes bcud len du'ang grags pa ste /
NK041(di)041:122: bdud rtsi a mri ta 'di nyid 'debs pa'i gzhi ma ni /
NK041(di)041:123: dza gad dpa' bo zhes chang rnam pa lnga yin te /
NK041(di)041:128: sbrang chang ste me tog gi chang dang lnga yin la /
NK041(di)041:129: de lta bu'i chang rnam pa lnga tshang ba'i gzhi
NK041(di)041:130: ma la gong gi bdud rtsi a mri ta btab
NK041(di)041:131: pa'i bdud rtsi sman mchod kyi yon tan ni /
NK041(di)041:133: bdud rtsi'i snod ni ka p+aa lar //
NK041(di)041:134: bcud ni byang chub sems kyi rgyun //
NK041(di)041:135: rkyen ni 'bru gsum nus pas byas //
NK041(di)041:136: don ni skye 'chi med pa la //
NK041(di)041:137: las ni rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba 'joms //
NK041(di)041:138: de phyir bdud rtsi a mri ta //
NK041(di)041:139: lha la phog na dgyes pa skong //
NK041(di)041:140: sring la phog na dam la 'du //
NK041(di)041:141: dgra la phog na thal bar rlog /
NK041(di)041:142: bgegs la phog na myos su 'jug /
NK041(di)041:143: rdzas la phog na nus pa bskyed //
NK041(di)041:144: gang la phog kyang stobs dang ldan //
NK041(di)041:146: deng sang gi cho ga mkhan po ba phal mo ches ni /
NK041(di)041:147: snod rnam pa gnyis su chang phud phal pa re
NK041(di)041:148: dang sha'am khrag thig pa re blug pa la byin
NK041(di)041:149: rlabs kyi tshig gshar re tsam ngag 'don byas pa
NK041(di)041:150: des bdud rtsi dang rak+ta'i go chod pa yin rgyu
NK041(di)041:151: rlom mod kyang / des ni lha tshogs thugs dam
NK041(di)041:152: bskang ba dang srung ma dam la 'du nus pa
NK041(di)041:153: rlom mod kyang / dka' zhing / de ma nus
NK041(di)041:154: tshe dgos don gyi dngos grub dang phrin las sogs
NK041(di)041:156: cho ga'i gzugs brnyan tsam du zad mod /
NK041(di)041:157: lha dang dam can 'du bar byed pa la sgrub
NK041(di)041:158: pa po dam tshig gtsang zhing lta dgongs dang ldan
NK041(di)041:159: pa / sngags tshig dang cho ga dag cing ting 'dzin gsal ba /
NK041(di)041:160: rdzas dang yo byad 'dzom zhing gtsang sbra thon pa sogs dgos par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK041(di)041:161: gnyis pa gtor ma'i go don ni /
NK041(di)041:162: gtor gzhong rin po che'i gzhal yas khang sa gzhi
NK041(di)041:163: dang mnyam pa'i nang du gtor ma nyid rdzas rang
NK041(di)041:164: ga ma'i rtog pa sbyong nas 'dod yon bdud rtsi'i
NK041(di)041:165: phung por rtogs par bya ba ste /
NK041(di)041:166: de yang yab yum thabs shes snang stong zung du
NK041(di)041:167: 'jug cing gnyis med bde ba chen po'i klong du
NK041(di)041:168: thugs dam yongs su skong bar byed pa'i dam rdzas
NK041(di)041:169: kyi gtso bo yin pas spyir btang dbus su bshams
NK041(di)041:170: dgos pa yang de ltar yin cing gong du smos
NK041(di)041:171: pa ltar ro // gsum pa rak+ta'i go don ni /
NK041(di)041:172: spyir rak+ta la rnam pa lnga ste /
NK041(di)041:173: srid pa gzhi'i rak+ta ni 'byung ba chu /
NK041(di)041:174: snang ba brda'i rak+ta ni kha dog dmar por gyur tshad /
NK041(di)041:175: 'gyur med don gyi rak+ta ni sor rtog ye shes kyi bdag nyid snang ba mtha' yas /
NK041(di)041:176: 'khor ba rgyu'i rak+ta ni ma'i mngal khrag /
NK041(di)041:177: 'bras bu chen po'i rak+ta ni gdug pa r+au tra bsgral ba'i snying khrag ste rnam pa lngar bshad /
NK041(di)041:178: de la dbye na rak+ta rtsa ba brgyad dang yan lag sum cu so lngar 'dus shing /
NK041(di)041:179: skabs don snying po mdor bsdus te bshad na /
NK041(di)041:182: gu h+ya rak+ta dang gsum ni bla med kyi cho ga gzhung phal che ba las 'byung ba ste /
NK041(di)041:183: de la ma h+aa rak+ta ni gdug pa can bsgral ba'i khrag chen po la 'jug kyang /
NK041(di)041:184: da lta ni dmigs rten tsam du srog chags g.yag
NK041(di)041:185: dang ra sogs kyi khrag gtsang mas rung mthun du
NK041(di)041:186: mdzad / m+au la rak+ta ni snod bcud chags pa'i
NK041(di)041:187: rgyu'i rtsa ba la 'jug kyang rung mthun chu gtsang
NK041(di)041:188: ma la sin+d+hu ra sogs rak+ta rtsa ba brgyad dang
NK041(di)041:189: yan lag gi rdzas rnams tshang ba'am ci 'byor ba
NK041(di)041:191: gu h+ya rak+ta ni mtshan ldan ma grong pa'i chos kyis ma gos pa'i pad+ma rak+ta la bshad do //
NK041(di)041:192: yang rnam pa gcig tu na m+au la rak+ta ni
NK041(di)041:193: spang bya dang gnyen po'i phyogs nas brjod na rten
NK041(di)041:194: 'brel bcu gnyis ni 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i rgyu yin
NK041(di)041:195: la / de nyid kyi rtsa ba ma rig pa
NK041(di)041:196: ste de rig pa'i ye shes kyis bcom pas 'khor
NK041(di)041:199: rgyu drug 'khor ba bsgral ba'i rak+tasa mchod //
NK041(di)041:201: gnyen po'i phyogs nas brjod na rgyu dug gsum dang
NK041(di)041:202: 'bras bu khams gsum du snang ba 'di thams cad
NK041(di)041:203: ye nas yum kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong du
NK041(di)041:204: rnam par dag pa ni rang byung bde ba chen
NK041(di)041:205: po'i rak+ta ste / ji skad du /
NK041(di)041:206: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK041(di)041:207: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi rang bzhin du //
NK041(di)041:208: khams gsum dug gsum bsgral ba'i rak+ta mchog /
NK041(di)041:210: legs ldan gyi rgyud las kyang /
NK041(di)041:211: ma h+aa rak+ta dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i khrag /
NK041(di)041:212: m+au la rak+ta rang byung pad+ma'i khrag /
NK041(di)041:213: chu dang ma 'dres dwangs ma'i khrag gis mchod //
NK041(di)041:215: bzhi pa sgron ma'i go don ni /
NK041(di)041:216: lus can thams cad la rang byung ye shes kyi
NK041(di)041:217: sgron ma rang chas su bzhugs pa nyid 'khor ba'i
NK041(di)041:218: d+r+wa bas bsgribs pa'i mun pa gzhoms pa'i ched du
NK041(di)041:219: lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i mar me'i mchod pa ste
NK041(di)041:220: / de yang sman bla'i mdo chog las /
NK041(di)041:222: mar me re re'i tshad kyang shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam du bya'o //
NK041(di)041:225: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i rang byung rang shar gyi
NK041(di)041:226: mchod pa de rnams ye nas sems can thams cad
NK041(di)041:227: la rang chas su gnas pa de nyid tshig gis
NK041(di)041:228: gsal btab ste dmigs med bde ba chen po'i dbyings
NK041(di)041:229: su thugs dam yongs su skong bar byed pa yin
NK041(di)041:230: no // de yang lta ba la bzla ba'i tshul
NK041(di)041:231: du rtogs tshig gis thugs dam yongs su skong bar
NK041(di)041:232: no // byed pa dang / sgom pa ting nge
NK041(di)041:233: 'dzin gyis rang bzhin gnas lugs las mi g.yo ba'i
NK041(di)041:234: tshul du thugs dam yongs su skong bar byed pa
NK041(di)041:235: no // byed pa dang / dang / lha rtog
NK041(di)041:236: dbyer med kyis gnas dag gnas gyur du thugs dam
NK041(di)041:237: yongs su skong bar byed pa dang gsum /
NK041(di)041:239: bskang ngo bskal pas thugs dam bskang //
NK041(di)041:241: de la bskang ngo zhes pas thugs dam yongs su skong tshig /
NK041(di)041:242: skong byed ni bskal pa ste /
NK041(di)041:243: rtogs tshig mang po'i don yin pas don dam gsal
NK041(di)041:244: 'debs kyi rtogs pa'i tshig mang po dag gis skong
NK041(di)041:245: ba'i don te / rong zom chos kyi bzang pos /
NK041(di)041:246: don dam gsal 'debs brjod pa tshig gi sgo //
NK041(di)041:248: dngos po stong nyid klong du bskang //
NK041(di)041:250: dngos por snang ba'i chos thams cad rang bzhin stong pa nyid las ma g.yos pa ste /
NK041(di)041:251: dbu ma rin chen phreng ba las /
NK041(di)041:252: bu ram rang bzhin mngar ba dang //
NK041(di)041:253: me yi rang bzhin tsha ba dang //
NK041(di)041:254: de bzhin chos rnams thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)041:255: rang bzhin stong pa nyid du gnas //
NK041(di)041:257: gnas lugs zab mo stong pa nyid kyi dang /
NK041(di)041:258: snang ba ye shes klong du bskang //
NK041(di)041:260: stong nyid de'i rtsal snang dag ma dag gi snang
NK041(di)041:261: ba thams cad ye shes chen po gcig gi klong
NK041(di)041:263: gsal ba shes rab klong du bskang //
NK041(di)041:264: zhes pa gong du smos pa'i thabs shes zung 'jug
NK041(di)041:265: bde chen stong nyid kyi ngo bo 'khor gsum mi
NK041(di)041:266: rtog pa'i shes rab kyi dang /
NK041(di)041:267: sdug bsngal chos nyid klong du bskang //
NK041(di)041:268: zhes pa gnas lugs ma rtogs par sdug bsngal gyis
NK041(di)041:269: bcings pa'i 'gro ba 'di rnams ye nas chos nyid
NK041(di)041:270: mnyam pa chen po'i klong du dag pa'i dang /
NK041(di)041:271: de bzhin du skye ba med pa'i sogs kyi don ni /
NK041(di)041:272: 'di ltar skyes pa ltar snang yang don la skye ba med pa'i dbyings su dang /
NK041(di)041:273: 'gags pa ltar snang yang don la 'gags pa med pa'i ye shes kyi mkha' klong du dang /
NK041(di)041:274: snang stong gi rang bzhin skye 'gag gi rnam pa
NK041(di)041:275: can de yang don la skye 'gags gnyis su med
NK041(di)041:276: pa'i chos nyid kyi klong du lta ba la bzla
NK041(di)041:278: nyams chag skong zhing rtog sgrib dag /
NK041(di)041:280: de yang nyin mtshan gyi drug cha'i nang du gnyen
NK041(di)041:281: pos ma sleb pas na thun tshod las 'das pa
NK041(di)041:283: zhag gcig gis bar ma chod pa 'gal ba dang /
NK041(di)041:284: zla bas bar ma chod pa tshun chad nyams pa dang /
NK041(di)041:285: lo gcig tshun chad 'das pa dang /
NK041(di)041:286: lo gsum tshun chad ral pa zhes dus la ltos nas rim gyis lci ba ste /
NK041(di)041:287: de tshun chad snying nas brtson pa chen pos bshags na 'dag la /
NK041(di)041:288: lo gsum 'das pa phan chad ni gsor mi rung ba dam tshig bkod pa'i rgyud las bshad do //
NK041(di)041:289: de la nyams pa la spyi mdo las /
NK041(di)041:290: nyams par gyur pa gang zhe na //
NK041(di)041:291: kun tu nyams pa chen po dang //
NK041(di)041:292: rtsa ba nyams dang yan lag nyams //
NK041(di)041:293: de bzhin zlas nyams zhar nyams lnga //
NK041(di)041:295: kun tu nyams pa chen po ni /
NK041(di)041:296: yul ches gnyan pa la kun dkris drag pos spyad
NK041(di)041:297: pa'ang lan grangs mang du byung ba dang dus 'das
NK041(di)041:298: ral pa la sogs pa yin la /
NK041(di)041:299: rtsa ba nyams pa dang yan lag nyams pa gnyis ni de dag dang /
NK041(di)041:301: nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i nyes pa dang /
NK041(di)041:303: gzhan gyi ngo dgar thal ba'i nyes pa'o //
NK041(di)041:306: rang gi sgo gsum yi dam gyi //
NK041(di)041:307: sku gsung thugs su mngon sbyar la //
NK041(di)041:308: rtag tu bzlas pa byed pa ni //
NK041(di)041:309: byang chub gzungs la zhugs pa yin //
NK041(di)041:310: rab kyis chu bo'i rgyun gzhung bzhin //
NK041(di)041:311: nyin gsum mtshan gsum gnyis gcig tu //
NK041(di)041:312: ma yengs tsam du ngang gis bzla //
NK041(di)041:313: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug dang //
NK041(di)041:314: dus bzhi'i bar du mi bcad cing //
NK041(di)041:315: tha mar brtson pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK041(di)041:316: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK041(di)041:317: brtson pas 'bad de mi byed na //
NK041(di)041:318: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK041(di)041:319: tshogs dang gtor ma'ang de bzhin du //
NK041(di)041:323: don dam blo rtog gi yul du byas pa'i sgrib pa ste /
NK041(di)041:325: don dam mi dmigs spros las 'das pas na //
NK041(di)041:327: de ltar blo'i dri ma rnams dag nas rang gnas
NK041(di)041:328: chos kyi rgyal srid la dbang bsgyur ba'i dbang dang
NK041(di)041:329: mchog thun gyi dngos grub rnam pa gnyis da lta
NK041(di)041:330: nyid du stsal du gsol zhes pa'o //
NK041(di)041:332: dang po bdud rtsis bskang ba ni /
NK041(di)041:335: kun gzhi mkha' klong yangs pa'i b+hany+dza'i snod du rang
NK041(di)041:336: byung byang chub kyi sems spros bral stong pa nyid
NK041(di)041:337: kyi bdud rtsis yongs su bkang nas sangs rgyas chos
NK041(di)041:338: kyi sku'i thugs dam gnas su skong ba dang /
NK041(di)041:341: sems nyid dmigs med kyi rtsal gdangs 'gags pa med
NK041(di)041:342: pa'i b+hany+dza'i snod du sems can gyi don la gzigs
NK041(di)041:343: pa sgrib pa med pa'i ye shes lnga'i rang byung
NK041(di)041:344: gi bdud rtsis yongs su bkang nas longs spyod rdzogs
NK041(di)041:345: sku'i thugs dam gnas su skong ba dang /
NK041(di)041:347: de las ma g.yos bzhin du mchog gi sprul pa'i
NK041(di)041:348: sku 'pho med 'od gsal gyi skur bzhengs pa phrin
NK041(di)041:349: las thugs rje'i b+hany+dza ru sems can rnams kyis chos
NK041(di)041:350: sku thig le byang chub kyi sems de'i sgrib pa
NK041(di)041:351: bsal bas sems nyid bde chen ye shes su 'bar
NK041(di)041:352: ba'i bdud rtsis bkang ba ni rgyal ba sprul sku'i
NK041(di)041:353: thugs dam gnas su skong ba dang /
NK041(di)041:354: ye shes rtsa lnga'i zhes sogs /
NK041(di)041:355: sems nyid kyi klong na 'bras bu'i chos ye shes
NK041(di)041:356: nyi shu rtsa lngar snang ba'i b+hany+dza ru sems nyid
NK041(di)041:357: kyi ngo bo a yig dkar po gnas pa de
NK041(di)041:358: lam pas nyams su blangs pas rgyal ba bzhi bcu
NK041(di)041:359: rtsa gnyis kyi lha tshogs su snang ba zhi ba
NK041(di)041:360: dang / dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i sogs te /
NK041(di)041:362: dpa' bo 'bru lnga 'od du 'bar ba'i b+hany+dza ru
NK041(di)041:363: shes rab yum lnga'i bdud rtsis yongs su bkang nas
NK041(di)041:364: zung 'jug ye shes kyi bdud rtsi de nyid gdul
NK041(di)041:365: bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i thabs kyi phyag rgya
NK041(di)041:366: khrag 'thung nga brgyad kyi rnam par shar ba khro
NK041(di)041:367: bo'i lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs dam gnas su skong
NK041(di)041:368: ba'o // bdud rtsi sman gyi dam tshig sogs //
NK041(di)041:369: 'di ltar 'khor 'das thams cad ye nas bdud rtsi'i
NK041(di)041:370: rang bzhin du gnas pa'i bdud rtsi sman gyi dam
NK041(di)041:371: tshig 'dis mchod 'os sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rgya
NK041(di)041:372: mtsho na bzhugs pa rnams kyi thugs dam skong ba'o
NK041(di)041:376: rang lus ye nas 'dod yon lnga'i rang bzhin gyi
NK041(di)041:377: gtor ma gdod nas grub pa tshig gis gsal btab
NK041(di)041:379: thod pa b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i gtor snod du shangs kyi
NK041(di)041:380: rlung sgrom sna'i dbang po nyid dpal bshos gtor ma'i
NK041(di)041:381: tshul du byas nas sna sgo'i las rlung ye shes
NK041(di)041:382: su dag pa'i 'dod yon drug gi lha mo 'dod
NK041(di)041:383: pa'i yon tan spro ba'i bdag nyid can gyi gtor
NK041(di)041:384: ma de la bde chen 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab ye
NK041(di)041:385: shes su 'bar ba'i sems dpa' bcu drug dang /
NK041(di)041:386: sems ma bcu drug gi mtheb kyus yongs su bskor ba la /
NK041(di)041:387: sgron ma mig gi dza gad stsal //
NK041(di)041:388: zhes pa sha lnga ni sgron ma ste /
NK041(di)041:389: dbang po lnga bkrag mdangs gzi brjid 'bar bar byed la /
NK041(di)041:390: de'i nang nas dbang po'i dwangs ma mig yin pas mig gi bdud rtsi dang /
NK041(di)041:391: dbang po lnga yi rak+ta ni /
NK041(di)041:392: chags 'dzin gyi sgo dbang shes nang du sdud pa'i
NK041(di)041:393: thabs dbang po lnga'i byed bcings kyis chags rtog dbyings
NK041(di)041:394: su bsgral ba'i rak+tasa brgyan te rang byung gi gtor
NK041(di)041:396: nyi zla kha sbyor gtor gzhong du //
NK041(di)041:398: spyi bo'i ham yig zla ba'i rang bzhin dang /
NK041(di)041:399: lte ba'i am yig nyi ma'i rang bzhin du yod
NK041(di)041:400: pa nyi zla kha sbyor gyi lus kyi dbus su
NK041(di)041:401: snying rang byung dpal gyi lha bshos su gtsug nas
NK041(di)041:402: snying ga'i rtsa chen brgyad pad 'dab brgyad kyi mtheb
NK041(di)041:403: kyu'i tshul du bskor nas rtsa de dag la gnas
NK041(di)041:404: pa'i rnam shes brgyad ni snying ga'i 'khor lo'i byed
NK041(di)041:405: pa bcings na ye shes lngar rang 'bar ba'i dza
NK041(di)041:406: gad bdud rtsi stsal nas de'i tshe rtsa chen bzhi
NK041(di)041:407: las 'khor ba 'char ba'i sgo 'gag pas 'khor ba
NK041(di)041:408: bsgral ba'i rak+tasa brgyan pa'i rang byung gi gtor ma
NK041(di)041:409: dang / khyab brdal lpags pa'i zhes sogs /
NK041(di)041:410: lus po'i lpags pa'i skya ris kyi ltems pa'i gtor
NK041(di)041:411: snod du rus pa'i tshogs rnams dpal gyi gtor mar
NK041(di)041:412: grub pa la sha'i mtheb kyu bkrag mdangs kyi bdud
NK041(di)041:413: rtsi khrag dang chu ser gyi rak+tasa brgyan pa'i gzugs
NK041(di)041:414: phung rang byung gi gtor ma dang /
NK041(di)041:415: khog pa stong ba'i zhes sogs /
NK041(di)041:416: lus khog gtor gzhong gi nang du mchin pa nyid
NK041(di)041:417: dpal bshos su btsugs pa la glo mtsher mkhal ma'i
NK041(di)041:418: mtheb kyus yongs su bskor nas /
NK041(di)041:420: gsang ba nang khrol du gtogs pa thams cad dza
NK041(di)041:421: gad bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du ye nas gnas pa'i
NK041(di)041:422: bdud rtsi dang / mkhris pa'i rak+ta ste nang phung
NK041(di)041:423: po'i chos thams cad ye nas rang byung gi gtor
NK041(di)041:424: tshogs su gnas pa'i ba ling 'dod yon lha mo
NK041(di)041:425: rdo rje'i dam tshig gis mchod pa'o //
NK041(di)041:426: gsum pa rak+tasa bskang ba ni /
NK041(di)041:429: spyi bor dung khang 'khor lo'i b+hany+dza ru sdug bsngal
NK041(di)041:430: gyis mtshon pa'i rnam par rtog pa thams cad mi
NK041(di)041:431: rtog pa'i dbyings su bsgral ba'i rak+tasa bkang nas dang
NK041(di)041:433: bza' btung sna tshogs kyi ro bcud nyams su myong
NK041(di)041:434: bar byed pa'i longs spyod 'khor lo'i b+hany+dza der dbang
NK041(di)041:435: po gzugs can lngas spyad byar ma gyur pa'i yul
NK041(di)041:436: 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi khams kyis bskyed
NK041(di)041:437: pa'i yid shes 'dzin med rgya yan gyi rak+tasa bkang
NK041(di)041:438: nas dang / snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i b+hany+dza
NK041(di)041:439: der chos nyid bsam brjod las 'das pa'i blo ngo
NK041(di)041:440: bo nyid du dag pa'i rak+tasa bkang nas dang /
NK041(di)041:441: lus kyi sprul gzhi lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i
NK041(di)041:442: b+hany+dza der nyon mongs pa srid pa'i rtsa ba dmar
NK041(di)041:443: cha rdul te shes rab stong nyid kyi rak+tasa bkang
NK041(di)041:444: nas dang / gsang gnas bde skyong 'khor lo'i b+hany+dza
NK041(di)041:445: der thabs shes mnyam par sbyor ba'i rjes chags bde
NK041(di)041:446: ba chen po'i thig le'i rak+tasa yongs su bkang nas
NK041(di)041:447: nas dang / dang / de ltar na ye nas
NK041(di)041:448: sems can thams cad la rak+ta bde ba chen po'i
NK041(di)041:449: ngo bor 'bar ba'i lha mo rdo rje'i dam tshig
NK041(di)041:450: gis mchod 'os rnams mnyes par byed pa'o //
NK041(di)041:451: bzhi pa sgron mes bskang ba ni /
NK041(di)041:453: bskang ngo sgron mes sogs te /
NK041(di)041:454: gzugs phung kun la khyab pa'i lpags pa'i kong bu
NK041(di)041:455: ru khrag dang chu ser gyi bcud kyi mar khus
NK041(di)041:456: yongs su gtams nas sha rus kyi sdong bu la
NK041(di)041:457: ye nas rang la ye shes rang gsal du gnas
NK041(di)041:458: pas lus kyi bkrag mdangs mchog tu 'bar ba'i zhun
NK041(di)041:459: mar rang byung gi sgron ma dang /
NK041(di)041:460: thod pa dung chen 'bar ba'i kong bur klad pa
NK041(di)041:461: go ro tsa na'i mar khus yongs su gtams te
NK041(di)041:462: shes bya'i gnas gsal bar byed pa'i dbang shes nyi
NK041(di)041:463: shu rtsa lnga'i sdong bu la dbang po sgo lnga'i
NK041(di)041:464: rang byung gi sgron ma dang /
NK041(di)041:465: tsit+ta snying gi kong bu 'bar ba'i snod du snying
NK041(di)041:466: tshil dkar dmar gyi mar khus yongs su gtams nas
NK041(di)041:467: snying gi rtsa chen brgyad pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi sdong
NK041(di)041:468: bu la rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar 'od
NK041(di)041:469: du 'bar ba'i rang byung gi sgron ma dang /
NK041(di)041:471: dbu ma ye shes kyi kong bu ru bde stong
NK041(di)041:472: gnyis med rang gsal 'od du 'bar ba'i mar khus
NK041(di)041:475: spyi bor bde chen gyi 'khor lo /
NK041(di)041:476: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi snying ga chos kyi lte
NK041(di)041:477: ba sprul pa'i spar bya me'i spar byed rlung gi
NK041(di)041:478: gsang gnas bde skyong gi 'khor lo ste bdun brtsegs
NK041(di)041:479: pa'i sdong bu la zhu bde las byung ba'i 'khor
NK041(di)041:480: 'das byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen por rang
NK041(di)041:481: 'bar ba'i rang byung gi sgron ma dang /
NK041(di)041:482: sems nyid mi shigs pa stong pa nyid kyi kong
NK041(di)041:483: bu ru chos thams cad skye med kyi dbyings su
NK041(di)041:484: la bzla ba'i mar khus yongs su gtams nas ma
NK041(di)041:485: rig pa la sogs te rten 'brel bcu gnyis 'char
NK041(di)041:486: byed kyi sgo rtsa phran bcu gnyis kyi sdong bu
NK041(di)041:487: la rig pa rang byung gi sgron ma rang 'bar
NK041(di)041:493: 'bras chos nyer lnga lus can rnams la rang chas
NK041(di)041:494: su gnas pa'i kong bu ru sems can gyi dbang
NK041(di)041:496: dbang po rab kyi tha ma dang /
NK041(di)041:502: rab kyi mthar phyin pa ste bdun dang /
NK041(di)041:503: de bzhin du dbang po 'bring gi tha ma sogs bdun dang /
NK041(di)041:504: tha ma'i tha ma sogs bdun tshan gsum ste nyi
NK041(di)041:505: shu rtsa gcig gi dbang po mi 'dra ba'i sems
NK041(di)041:506: nyid a dkar dri ma med pa nyer gcig gi
NK041(di)041:507: mar khus yongs su gtams nas a yig de rnams
NK041(di)041:508: kyi klong na 'bras chos nyer lnga 'char rung ma
NK041(di)041:509: 'gags par gnas pa'i sdong bu la shes rab 'bru
NK041(di)041:510: lnga ste / m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams 'od
NK041(di)041:511: du zhu ba yum lnga'i ngo bor 'bar ba'i sgron
NK041(di)041:512: lnga ste / ma dang / mchog sangs rgyas kyi
NK041(di)041:513: zhing khams 'od gsal rgya tshad dang bral ba'i kong
NK041(di)041:514: bu ru de'i rang mdangs 'gags med bde stong gnyis
NK041(di)041:515: med kyi mar khus yongs su gtams nas chos thams
NK041(di)041:516: cad zung 'jug ye shes kyi thig le gcig tu
NK041(di)041:517: 'khyil ba'i sdong bu la ye shes rnam pa lnga
NK041(di)041:518: rang shar du 'bar ba'i sgron ma dang /
NK041(di)041:519: 'khor 'das thams cad kyi 'byung khung kun gzhi ma
NK041(di)041:520: bcos mkha' klong yangs pa'i kong bu ru chos dbyings
NK041(di)041:521: 'gyur ba med pa'i mar khus yongs su gtams nas
NK041(di)041:522: byang chub kyi sems dri ma med pa'i sdong bu
NK041(di)041:523: la chos longs sprul gsum mngon byang rdo rje'i sku
NK041(di)041:524: ste sku lnga lhun grub 'od du 'bar ba'i sgron
NK041(di)041:525: ma ste / de ltar lus can rnams la ye
NK041(di)041:526: nas rang byung gi sgron ma rang 'bar du gnas
NK041(di)041:527: pa'i gnas lugs kyi don 'di las mi 'da' ba'i
NK041(di)041:528: ma ste / dam tshig ste / rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK041(di)041:529: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK041(di)041:530: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK041(di)041:532: d+ai pa pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aas mchod 'os rnams la
NK041(di)041:533: mar me'i mchod pa'i gzhi tshugs zhes pa'i don no
NK041(di)041:534: // e ho sogs khrus bdun gyi rig sngags lan
NK041(di)041:535: bdun bzlas pas 'byung ba'i yi ge de rnams lus
NK041(di)041:536: can rnams la rang chas su yod pa 'od du
NK041(di)041:537: 'bar bas chag nyams dang rtog sgrib thams cad dag
NK041(di)041:541: khro bo gnas gyur gyi bskang pa gnyis las /
NK041(di)041:544: yid kyi rnam shes gnas dag pa //
NK041(di)041:546: yid ni rtog bcas 'khor ba'i byed pa po dang /
NK041(di)041:547: rtog med myang 'das gnyis ka'i byed pa po kun bzang gi ngo bor gnas su dag pa dang /
NK041(di)041:548: yid kyis gtan la dbab bya'i yul chos kyi khams
NK041(di)041:549: de kun tu bzang mo'i ngo bor rnam par dag
NK041(di)041:550: pa dang / de bzhin du phung po lnga ni rgyal ba rigs lnga'i ngo bor dang /
NK041(di)041:551: 'byung ba lnga ni yum lnga'i ngo bor dang /
NK041(di)041:552: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ni sems dpa' brgyad /
NK041(di)041:553: de'i yul brgyad ni sems ma brgyad dang /
NK041(di)041:557: de gsum 'dus pa'i lus te reg pa ste lus
NK041(di)041:558: kyi chos bzhi ni sgo ba bzhi'i ngo bor dang
NK041(di)041:559: / rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi ni khro mo lcags
NK041(di)041:560: kyu ma la sogs pa bzhi'i ngo bor gnas su
NK041(di)041:566: zhe sdang ste nyon mongs drug ni thub drug gi ngo bor gnas su dag pa'o //
NK041(di)041:572: phrag dog ste dug lnga khrag 'thung yab lnga'i ngo bor dang /
NK041(di)041:573: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' ste 'byung ba yul lnga ni khrag 'thung yum lnga'i ngo bor dang /
NK041(di)041:574: lus zhes pa ni 'byung ba lngas 'khor ba'i gnas
NK041(di)041:575: skabs su 'khor ba 'byung khungs sam de'i rten gzhi
NK041(di)041:577: myang 'das kyi gnas su 'bras chos thams cad kyi
NK041(di)041:578: 'byung khungs sam rten gzhi yum lnga 'dus pa kun
NK041(di)041:579: tu bzang mo chos kyi sku ste /
NK041(di)041:580: dkon mchog sgron me'i mdo las /
NK041(di)041:581: chos kyi sku ni rgyal ba rnams kyi lus //
NK041(di)041:584: sbyor ba'i dbyings nas phyin ci log gi rtog pa dang /
NK041(di)041:585: sgrol ba'i dbyings nas reg bya'i rtog pa dang /
NK041(di)041:586: dam tshig gi dbyings nas myong byed kyi rtog pa dang /
NK041(di)041:587: gsang ba'i dbyings nas skye gnas kyi rtog pa bzhi 'joms pa'i he ru ka bzhi'i ngo bor dang /
NK041(di)041:591: mngal skyes te skye gnas bzhi'i rtog pa ni he ru ka bzhi'i yum bzhi'i ngo bor dang /
NK041(di)041:592: yul rnam par rig pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshogs brgyad ni khro mo goo ri ma brgyad dang /
NK041(di)041:593: de'i yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos dang /
NK041(di)041:594: khams dang skye mched de rnam 'gyur yul brgyad ni
NK041(di)041:595: khro mo ste sid+ha ma brgyad kyi ngo bor dang
NK041(di)041:599: mtshan ma'i mtha' ste bzhi ni rdo rje sring 'gro
NK041(di)041:600: ma la sogs pa khro mo sgo ma bzhi'i ngo
NK041(di)041:601: bor dang / rtog tshogs sna tshogs su snang ba ni /
NK041(di)041:602: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo la sogs te
NK041(di)041:603: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi ngo bor dang
NK041(di)041:604: / de ltar dag pa'i ye shes kyi lha tshogs
NK041(di)041:605: thams cad chos sku 'gyur ba med pa rdo rje
NK041(di)041:606: mi shigs pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang gzugs sku
NK041(di)041:607: gang 'dul zhi khro'i lha tshogs kyi rol par snang
NK041(di)041:608: nas 'gags med gsung gi snang ba gdul bya'i blo
NK041(di)041:609: dang 'tshams par sna tshogs su snang yang sku la
NK041(di)041:611: gsung thugs 'khrul pa med pa dang /
NK041(di)041:612: yon tan mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor sad par byas te /
NK041(di)041:613: phrin las 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du 'gro
NK041(di)041:614: ba'i spyi gtsug 'khor lo'i rgyan du zhugs pa'i mchod
NK041(di)041:615: yul ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i rol pa zad mi
NK041(di)041:616: shes par bzhugs pa rnams thugs dam yongs su skong
NK041(di)041:617: nas rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi nyams chag dang rtog
NK041(di)041:618: sgrib dag nas skong ba'i 'bras bu dbang bzhi'i ye
NK041(di)041:619: shes dang mchog thun gyi dngos grub dam pa da
NK041(di)041:620: lta nyid du stsal du gsol zhes pa'o //
NK041(di)041:621: zhes skong gi bshad pa mdor bsdus su byas pa
NK041(di)041:622: 'di ni rje bla ma 'gyur med rin chen rnam
NK041(di)041:623: par rgyal ba'i sde'i bka' lung spyi bor lhungs pa
NK041(di)041:624: ldog par ma nus pas smin gling grwa pa'i tha
NK041(di)041:625: shal du gyur pa d+harma kirtisa gang shes tshod dpogs
NK041(di)041:626: su bris pa las gzhung don dang 'byor ba ji
NK041(di)041:627: bzhin byung min 'gro ba chos spyan gyis gzigs pas
NK041(di)041:629: 'phags bod mkhas grub du ma'i thugs kyi bcud //
NK041(di)041:630: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba 'gyod tshangs bshags skong la //
NK041(di)041:631: zin ma t+aika su byas pa'i dge 'bras gang //
NK041(di)041:632: 'gro kun byang chub thob pa'i rgyur bsngo'o //
NK041(di)041:633: 'dis kyang gsang chen rnying ma'i bstan pa rin po che dar rgyas su gyur cig /
